<Base title="THE ROAD" description="NARROW. — heavyweight streetwear rooted in the oldest texts on earth. Pressed by hand in the UK, released in small numbers.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>THE ROAD</h1>
    <p class="big">Most gates are wide. Wide is easy. Wide is trending. Wide is whatever everyone else is wearing.</p>
    <p class="big">NARROW. is the other gate.</p>
    <p>We make heavyweight streetwear rooted in the oldest texts on earth — pressed by hand in the UK, released in small numbers, gone when they're gone. Every drop tells one story from the source material. No borrowed hype. No logos for the sake of logos. Just weight — in the fabric and in the words.</p>
    <p>This isn't merch. Nobody licensed this. One person, one press, one conviction: that the hardest road is the one worth dressing for.</p>
    <p class="final">The gate is narrow. Few find it.<br />You just did.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
